            <div class="why-body">
              <h4>Zero Surgical Risk</h4>
              <p>No anaesthesia, no incisions, no post-operative complications — just targeted, effective treatment.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-syringe"></i></div>
            <div class="why-body">
              <h4>Regenerative Approach</h4>
              <p>PRP and bone marrow therapies harness your own body's healing mechanisms for lasting results.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i></div>
            <div class="why-body">
              <h4>Cost Effective</h4>
              <p>Non-surgical treatments cost a fraction of surgery — with comparable or better outcomes for most
                conditions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-hands-holding-child"></i></div>
            <div class="why-body">
              <h4>Personalised Care Plans</h4>
              <p>Every patient receives an individualised treatment pathway tailored to their specific condition and
